      • fromBinary

        public static CodePointTrie.Small fromBinary​(CodePointTrie.ValueWidth valueWidth,
                                             ByteBuffer bytes)
        Creates a trie from its binary form. Same as CodePointTrie.fromBinary(Type, ValueWidth, ByteBuffer) with CodePointTrie.Type.SMALL.
        Parameters:
        valueWidth - selects the number of bits in a data value; this method throws an exception if the valueWidth does not match the binary data; use null to accept any data value width
        bytes - a buffer containing the binary data of a CodePointTrie
        Returns:
        the trie
